{"tid":420650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我生日我親戚送左個袋比我","createTime":"2017-10-01T14:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T16:05:06.000Z","uid":76939,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4b9fbcc5a7455fbf77153dc287a6eba7f6d3b2f4","tid":420650,"uid":76939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:55:07.000Z","msg":"話說今日一家日一齊食飯，慶祝國慶同埋我就生日，慶祝埋。之後我姨姨送左個袋比我做生日禮物，個袋我認得係之前我表哥（姨姨個仔）話買錯左，諗住1000$賣比我。<br />\n之後走個陣仲走過黎話係champion ,好多男仔都覺得型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哦左一句。<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁靚，益左你<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比我就當面屌柒佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/225317_73193764577347a8dbc586b1aa97d47c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F225317_73193764577347a8dbc586b1aa97d47c.jpg&h=dbc2e96e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8d001b494d6871eb8afb4567a02fdf4cd1c936f","tid":420650,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c76ada78b460409472481f6a28aaf042f3872fd","tid":420650,"uid":76939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>右個袋係咩樣？有冇圖？</blockquote><br />\n岩岩load 到"},{"pid":"e94223294123beb8dab9fb3387a97ded08c7e40c","tid":420650,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:02:18.000Z","msg":"成個春袋咁"},{"pid":"622bfb9d835978d2800e7ba78537b3c013c714e0","tid":420650,"uid":75694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"是q 但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3579bea4f82dd64dacccd60236e6bf1df4c18620","tid":420650,"uid":76939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成個春袋咁</blockquote>